           def self.search(search)
        
      284. 
      
        
    284. 
          1
          
            if search
        
      285. 
      
        
    285. 
          
          
              s=search.scan(/\S+/)
        
      286. 
      
        
    286. 
          
          
              case s.size
        
      287. 
      
        
    287. 
          
          
                when 1
        
      288.

                   where('surname LIKE ?', "%#{s[0]}%")
        
      289. 
      
        
    289. 
          
          
                when 2
        
      290. 
      
        
    290. 
          
          
                  where('surname LIKE ? and name LIKE ?',"#{s[0]}","#{s[1]}")
        
      291. 
      
        
    291. 
          
          
                when 3
        
      292. 
      
        
    292. 
          
          
                  where('surname LIKE ? and name LIKE ? and father_name LIKE ?',"#{s[0]}","#{s[1]}","#{s[2]}")
        
      293.

                else
        
      294. 
      
        
    294. 
          
          
                  scoped.order(:surname)
        
      295.
